statements: SELECT * FROM website_visitors;
SELECT visitor_id, visited_page FROM website_visitors WHERE ip_address = '127.0.0.1';
SELECT DISTINCT ip_address FROM website_visitors ORDER BY visit_timestamp DESC;
SELECT referral_source, COUNT(visitor_id) AS visitor_count FROM website_visitors GROUP BY referral_source HAVING visitor_count > 1;
SELECT * FROM website_visitors WHERE visit_timestamp BETWEEN '2022-01-01' AND '2022-01-31' ORDER BY visit_timestamp ASC;
SELECT * FROM website_visitors WHERE visitor_id = 1;
SELECT ip_address, visited_page FROM website_visitors WHERE visit_timestamp BETWEEN '2022-01-01' AND '2022-02-01';
